Noshi Gilani Collection

Noshi Gilani

Noshi Gilani is a famous female poet belonging from Pakistan. She was born in Bahawalpur city. She has written few poetry books which include Mohabatain Jab Sumar Kurna, Udas Honay Kay Din Naheen, Pehla Lafz Mohabat Likha, Hum Tera Intezaar Kurtey Rahey and Hawa Chupke se Kehti Hai. Keep visiting us for more Noshi Gilani Poetry.

Tujh se judaa hona zaroori ho geya hai..

Noshi Gilani

Khayaal-o-Khwaab Ke Manzar Sajaana Chahta Hai

Noshi Gilani

KaheeN KartAy Nahi izhaaR, ChuP Hain

Noshi Gilani

Aankhain Bhi Wohi Hain Tou Dareecha Bhi Wohi Hai

Noshi Gilani

Ye Umar Bhar Ka Safar aur Ye Raaigaani Teri

Noshi Gilani

Safar Malaal Ka Hai Aur Chal Rahi Huun Mei

Noshi Gilani

Kuchi Bhi Kar Guzarnay Mein Dair Kitni Lagti Hai

Noshi Gilani

Dard Ki Ley Maddham Tou Ho

Noshi Gilani

Bila Jawaaz Rakhain Khud Ko Beqaraar Bhee Kiun ?

Noshi Gilani

Mout Se Mukar Jaayein, Zindagi Se Dar Jaayein..

Noshi Gilani
